snippet.title: 【ANTICHAMBER】ヾ( ･`⌓´･)ﾉﾞ WE CAN DO IT
snippet.description:
LETS BEAT THIS
【Please read the following rules so we can all have fun】

►Be respectful to each other
►Don't spam excessively 
►DO NOT TYPE YOUR WHOLE MESSAGE IN ALL CAPS LOCK LIKE THIS 
►Don't raid others OR discuss me in other channels unless I am explicitly brought up
►Try not to backseat*
►If you see people doing any of the above, just try to ignore it and enjoy the stream! Or at least poke fun at them respectfully :)

*I like to play games my own way: mostly by learning through experience and being wrong. Sometimes, I will ask for help and even then, I may choose not to take your advice. Launch the game yourself if you want to see it played your way or at least pay money to yell at me (」ﾟﾛﾟ)｣$$$

Reading chat is part of the fun and why I love streaming, if you refuse to follow the rules, then you just won't be able to join in. 

https://twitter.com/watsonameliaEN
#amelive #hololiveEnglish #holoMyth #ameliaRT

This game is being streamed and monetized after confirmation with Demruth.
